"title": "2036: Jesus Christ, humility of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "2036",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The obedient submission of Jesus Christ to his Father, seen in his willingness to become a human being for humanity's sake, his freedom from self-interest and his willingness to serve others.</p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's willingness to become a human being</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:6-Phil2:7\">PHP 2:6–2:7</a></strong> <em>“human likeness” is not mere similarity to but identity with humanity.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:3\">ROM 8:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:9\">2CO 8:9</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's humility predicted in the OT</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:19-Matt12:20\">MAT 12:19–12:20</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:2-Isa42:3\">ISA 42:2–42:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa50:4-Isa50:6\">ISA 50:4–50:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:17\">MAT 8:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:32-Acts8:33\">ACT 8:32–8:33</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:2-Isa53:7\">ISA 53:2–53:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:22\">1PE 2:22</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:9\">ISA 53:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:24\">1PE 2:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:5\">MAT 21:5</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:15\">JHN 12:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech9:9\">ZEC 9:9</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech12:10\">ZEC 12:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:31\">MAT 26:31</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:27\">MRK 14:27</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech13:7\">ZEC 13:7</a></p>\n<h2>The poverty of Jesus Christ's birth and upbringing</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:7\">LUK 2:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:12\">LUK 2:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:16\">LUK 2:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:22-Luke2:24\">LUK 2:22–2:24</a> <em>Only the poorest families offered doves or pigeons.</em></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's obedience to his human parents</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:51\">LUK 2:51</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's obedience to his heavenly Father</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:30\">JHN 5:30</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:29\">JHN 8:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:10\">JHN 15:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:19\">ROM 5:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:3\">ROM 15:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:8\">PHP 2:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb5:8\">HEB 5:8</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's dependence on his heavenly Father</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:19\">JHN 5:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:30\">JHN 5:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:7\">JHN 17:7</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's submission to baptism</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt3:13-Matt3:15\">MAT 3:13–3:15</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:9\">MRK 1:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:21\">LUK 3:21</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's humble acceptance of ill treatment</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:23\">1PE 2:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:63\">MAT 26:63</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:61\">MRK 14:61</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:66-Matt26:67\">MAT 26:66–26:67</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:64-Mark14:65\">MRK 14:64–14:65</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:14\">MAT 27:14</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:5\">MRK 15:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:28-Matt27:30\">MAT 27:28–27:30</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:17-Mark15:19\">MRK 15:17–15:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:2\">JHN 19:2</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's acceptance of the cross</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:8\">PHP 2:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:39\">MAT 26:39</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:36\">MRK 14:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:42\">LUK 22:42</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:53\">MAT 26:53</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:34\">LUK 23:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb5:7\">HEB 5:7</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's humility with other people</h2>\n<p>Children:\n <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:13-Matt19:15\">MAT 19:13–19:15</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:13-Mark10:16\">MRK 10:13–10:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:15-Luke18:17\">LUK 18:15–18:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt20:29-Matt20:34\">MAT 20:29–20:34</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:46-Mark10:52\">MRK 10:46–10:52</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:35-Luke18:43\">LUK 18:35–18:43</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:40-Mark1:42\">MRK 1:40–1:42</a> <em>Leprosy sufferers</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:5-John4:9\">JHN 4:5–4:9</a> <em>a Samaritan woman</em></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's servant attitude</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:45\">MRK 10:45</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt20:28\">MAT 20:28</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:19-Matt12:20\">MAT 12:19–12:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:4-John13:5\">JHN 13:4–13:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:12\">JHN 13:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor10:1\">2CO 10:1</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's teaching about humility</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:33-Mark9:37\">MRK 9:33–9:37</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:1-Matt18:5\">MAT 18:1–18:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:46-Luke9:48\">LUK 9:46–9:48</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:8-Matt23:12\">MAT 23:8–23:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:42-Mark10:45\">MRK 10:42–10:45</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt20:26-Matt20:28\">MAT 20:26–20:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke14:7-Luke14:11\">LUK 14:7–14:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:9-Luke18:14\">LUK 18:9–18:14</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's humility as a model for others</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:12-John13:17\">JHN 13:12–13:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:29-Matt11:30\">MAT 11:29–11:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:25\">EPH 5:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:5\">PHP 2:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:21\">1PE 2:21</a></p>",
